fields.value: Computational Chemistry Data for Small Molecules

dsDescriptionValue.value: Data associated with computational chemistry program output for a selection of mostly small molecules.

keywordVocabulary.value: DFT, MP2, CI, computational chemistry, quantum, hydrogen, boron trifluoride, carbon dioxide, carbon monoxide, ethene, 1,3-butadiene, ethyne, formaldehyde, fullerene, nitrogen dioxide, sulfur dioxide, formaldehyde, nitrogen, aluminium trichloride, water, ethylene, benzene, ammonia, hydrocarbon, acetylene, cyclopropane, cyclopropene cation, molecular orbitals, NBO, excited states, TDDFT, CCSD(T), aurora borealis

fields.value: Filenames used are arbitrary. When point group symmetry was taken into consideration (i.e. not 'C1'), the point group symmetry and input coordinates were determined with Gabedit 2.4.8. For example, a detected Dinfh (D_infinity_h) symmetry was specified  as Dnh 4 (D4h); please see the file metadata. Please check geometry co-ordinate data carefully when comparing the same molecules with different calculations.
